PLEASE NOTE: There is a buyzone in this map, weapons are NOT stripped and DEagles are not given.

A map inspired obviously by the deagle maps. I made it specifically for a couple friends of mine. A few custom textures which are included in the BSP. Hope you all have fun playing the map!
